## Technical Requirements

### Architecture Approach
Blueprint.js v6 supports dark mode via the `.bp5-dark` class on a parent element.
We will:
1. Add dark mode CSS variable overrides in globals.css
2. Create a ThemeProvider/ThemeContext for state management
3. Add toggle button in Navigation
4. Persist preference to localStorage

